<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NestJS Auth Demo - Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2 class="text-center">NestJS Authentication Concepts Demo</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="lead text-center">
                            This application demonstrates different authentication concepts in a NestJS app.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="row mt-4">
                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <div class="card mb-4 auth-feature-card">
                                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                                        <h3 class="mb-0">Basic Authentication</h3>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>Demonstration of Basic Authentication with password hashing.</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Username/password authentication using HTTP headers</li>
                                            <li>Password hashing with bcrypt</li>
                                            <li>Implementation using NestJS Guards</li>
                                            <li>Secure password storage</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                                            <a href="/auth/basic" class="btn btn-primary">Try Basic Authentication</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h4>Coming Soon</h4>
                            <p>The following authentication methods will be implemented in future updates:</p>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="card mb-3 auth-feature-card">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h5 class="card-title">JWT Authentication</h5>
                                            <p class="card-text">Token-based authentication using JSON Web Tokens.</p>
                                            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" disabled>Coming Soon</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="card mb-3 auth-feature-card">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h5 class="card-title">Session Authentication</h5>
                                            <p class="card-text">Form-based authentication with server-side sessions.</p>
                                            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" disabled>Coming Soon</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="card mb-3 auth-feature-card">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h5 class="card-title">OAuth 2.0 / OIDC</h5>
                                            <p class="card-text">Authentication using third-party identity providers.</p>
                                            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" disabled>Coming Soon</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h4>API Endpoints</h4>
                            <p>The following API endpoints are available for testing:</p>
                            <div class="table-responsive">
                                <table class="table table-striped">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th>Endpoint</th>
                                            <th>Method</th>
                                            <th>Authentication</th>
                                            <th>Description</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><code>/</code></td>
                                            <td>GET</td>
                                            <td>None</td>
                                            <td>Home page (this page)</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><code>/auth/basic</code></td>
                                            <td>GET</td>
                                            <td>Basic Auth</td>
                                            <td>Protected endpoint using Basic Authentication</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h4>Testing Basic Authentication</h4>
                            <p>You can test the Basic Authentication endpoint using curl:</p>
                            <div class="bg-light p-3 rounded">
                                <pre>curl -v -u admin:secret http://localhost:3000/auth/basic</pre>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mt-2">Default credentials:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Username: <code>admin</code></li>
                                <li>Password: <code>secret</code></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                        <p class="mb-0 text-center">This is an educational demo. <strong>Do not use in production</strong> without proper security review.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 